  "description": "A nighttime scene depicts a tranquil waterfront with brightly lit houses reflected in the dark water. A rocky breakwater occupies the foreground, leading the eye toward the illuminated buildings. The houses vary in style and color, creating a charming and picturesque coastal view. Several boats are docked near the houses, adding to the scene's maritime atmosphere. A tall palm tree stands prominently in front of one of the houses. The sky is a deep blue, typical of a clear night, and the reflections of the lights create shimmering trails in the water. The overall impression is one of peacefulness and beauty.",
